text: Eloise Mumford (born September 24, 1986) is an American actress. She played Sue Lawson in Drones. She played Kate Kavanagh in Fifty Shades of Grey. The actress was born in Olympia, Washington. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Washington (state) Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:People from Olympia, Washington
